snippet.textDisplay:
There's a family feud episode that will ALWAYS leave me baffled forever! Basically it was the bonus round at the end where you have 20-25 secs to answer. The question was: what country is known to have THE WORST food? The first dude said: France, and the second dude said: Italy.

I...could not believe what I was hearing/seeing. According to them, France and Italy have the worst food ever?! They are the two countries known for the BEST FOOD!! The top answers were England and Scotland I think, but...wow. The ignorance was strong in this family. 😐😐😐😅
